author: Boston Shoe Fanatic (on a budget)
title: Boston Shoe Fanatic (on a budget)
text: they have a good number of very good olive oils, but not what one would call a broad selection of the best. their prices are a bit high, even in comparison with the generally very high prices one must pay in the u.s. for top quality olive oil (which generally costs about half as much in europe). service was fast and shipping good.
